{"name":"Shadowlark","size":"medium","type":"plant","tag":"Fenwick, Castino","alignment":"Neutral Evil","hitDice":"6","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"39 (6d8 + 12)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"8","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"8","blindsight":"60","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Genetic Drift","desc":"_Undefined_ is immune to Shadow Touch."}],"actions":[{"name":"Life Drain","desc":"The [MON]'s shadowy roots tangle around a creature within 60ft. and drains the life out of them. [DEX ATK] to hit. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D8] necrotic damage. The [MON] heals for the damage it dealt."},{"name":"Shadow Touch","desc":"The [MON] summons a shadowy vine that saps the energy out of a creature within 60ft. Make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Charisma Save. Upon failure, the creature takes [DEX 1d6] necrotic damage and loses 2 STR + 2 CON for the next hour. If a creature has 0 STR, it is incapacitated. If a creature has 0 CON, it dies."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Camouflage","desc":"The [MON] can hide in the dark as a bonus action."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"nature","stat":"int"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}